oggle='popover' data-placement='top'>بَطِرَتۡ مَعِيشَتَهَاۖ</a> فَتِلۡكَ مَسَٰكِنُهُمۡ لَمۡ تُسۡكَن </div><div>مِّنۢ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بَعۡدِهِمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> إِلَّا قَلِيلٗاۖ وَكُنَّا نَحۡنُ ٱلۡوَٰرِثِينَ ٨٥ وَمَا كَانَ </div><div>رَبُّكَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مُهۡلِكَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلۡقُرَىٰ حَتَّىٰ يَبۡعَثَ فِيٓ أُمِّهَا رَسُولٗا يَتۡلُواْ </div><div>عَلَيۡهِمۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ءَايَٰتِنَاۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَمَا كُنَّا مُهۡلِكِي ٱلۡقُرَىٰٓ إِلَّا وَأَهۡلُهَا ظَٰلِمُونَ </div><div>٩٥</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
